column5: Met up with Christopher k.and his dad. Fished 100 FOW, marked some fish but couldn't induce a bite. Ice was about 7-8" thick.  It was still a great day to get out and meet another OFNer.
Good to meet you too Stan, got my first hut today and hope to be getting out much more
I've met a few,sure a great bunch!
Sorry the bite wasn't on. But even just getting out is always nice. What hut did you get chris?
Great choice in hut Chris you will be happy with it for years to come.
